parameters: Would you like to view the event? It's for the quota!
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Ugh... What should I do... What should I do...

\nc<Saki>Quite the opposite. I've used up so much energy learning the
job that I'm behind on this period's quota...

\nc<Senpai>Honestly, you need to calculate and manage your energy
consumption properly.

\nc<Saki>Isn't there some responsibility on the part of a senpai who
takes energy under the guise of training fees...
\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>Oh? Saki, your true feelings are showing.
\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Ah! Se-se-senpai! You misunderstand! That was just...

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>How refreshing. It's rare to be told off to my face. Well,
I'll let it slide just this once.

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>Honestly, it's rare to have a boss who teaches you skills in
exchange for energy. Other teams' bosses don't teach at all,
and you have to learn by watching.

\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Whaaat... Is that so?! You're right, Senpai! (Indeed, it's
better than not learning anything at all...)
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Anyway, I need energy. Isn't there any big event coming up?

\nc<Senpai>Even if you say so... All the good events have mostly been
snapped up. There are more than one or two cases like
Saki's.

\nc<Senpai>The only event that could give you a large amount of energy
would be an orgy event... but those are rare.

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>Most clients prefer one-on-one enjoyment. Orgies are
considered special events.
\nc<Saki>That does seem to be the case... So there's no other way?

\nc<Senpai>Who knows. There aren't any insatiable clients among today's
reservations.

\nc<Saki>(Ugh, why is it that when I need it the most, there's none
available...)

\nc<Senpai>There are plenty of regular clients, so why not milk them
for all they're worth? You're not trying to have fun as
usual anyway.

\nc<Senpai>I'll set up today's reservations on a time limit for you.
I'll arrange a selection of clients... the rest is up to you
to handle well.
